{
  "texts": [
    "We propose an experimental toolkit in which certain parameters of synchrony behaviors of SIAs can be specifically manipulated in a controlled manner, such as time-lag.",
    "Such a toolkit would facilitate the resource-intensive character of synchrony research, enable experimental manipulations, and help to derive practical recommendations.",
    "Frontiers in Psychiatry frontiersin.org",
    "Wessler et al.",
    "10.3389/fpsyt.2024.1330158 Frontiers in Psychiatry frontiersin.org"
  ]
}